data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought after SW Cape! This meticulously maintained 3 BR/2 BA residence offers a perfect blend of style and UPGRADED functionality featuring cathedral ceilings and porcelain tile throughout. The interior boasts built-ins for convenient storage, while California closets add a touch of luxury to every bedroom.  Step into your oasis with a SOLAR-HEATED SALT WATER POOL embraced by a screened-in lanai featuring a built-in bar - an entertainer's delight! The fenced yard provides security for pets, & a shed for extra storage. The garage has custom storage cabinets & painted floor.  The exterior has soffit lights for a finishing touch.  Enjoy peace of mind with IMPACT WINDOWS & A NEW ROOF. This gem is NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE, ensuring security & affordability. The large eat-in kitchen is perfect for gatherings, equipped with a double oven range for culinary enthusiasts.  Don't miss the chance to call this house your home - a perfect blend of comfort, style, & Florida living. Desirable location, close proximity to Veterans Parkway, shopping & dining.  Act now, as this property is sure to capture the hearts of those seeking the best in Florida living!
